      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是默认状态。HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault是外部安全存储系统，Active状态可以访问它，但不需要画返回箭头——数据推送到Vault后分析器继续留在Active状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Active",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
