      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来构建。把HealthTech_LabAnalyzer作为起始节点，连接到Idle状态，然后Idle通过Start事件转换到Active，Active通过Stop回到Idle，同时Active有一条线连到HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。",
      "elements_involved": [
